    {
      "id": "62e493eae60035000031866b",
      "text": "[https://blog.goo.ne.jp/masaoreport/e/719c5c74655c6cf33b360538a3a85fb8 聖痴愚の系譜 - 団塊亭日常]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659147243,
      "updated": 1659147243
    },
    {
      "id": "62e493eae60035000031866c",
      "text": "　このブログの主張するところでは",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659147243,
      "updated": 1659147243
    },
    {
      "id": "62e493eae60035000031866d",
      "text": "　　[遠藤周作]のいくつかの作品に登場する人物(省略)",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659147243,
      "updated": 1659147243
    },
    {
      "id": "62e493eae60035000031866e",
      "text": "　　「[海辺のカフカ]」([村上春樹])のナカタさん",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659147243,
      "updated": 1659147526
    },
    {
      "id": "62e493eae60035000031866f",
      "text": "　　映画「道」のジェルソミーナ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659147243,
      "updated": 1659147243
    },
    {
      "id": "62e493eae600350000318670",
      "text": "　　[常不軽菩薩]（[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%8D%E8%BB%BD%E8%8F%A9%E8%96%A9 常不軽菩薩 - Wikipedia]）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659147243,
      "updated": 1659147243
    },
    {
      "id": "62e493eae600350000318671",
      "text": "　　[ドンキホーテ]（[ドン・キホーテ]）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659147243,
      "updated": 1659147243
    },
    {
      "id": "62e493eae600350000318672",
      "text": "　も聖痴愚の系譜に連なるものである、らしい",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659147243,
      "updated": 1659147243
